# Expo's CLI + Metro plugins assume a hoisted `node_modules` layout
# (transitive deps like `expo-asset` resolvable from the package
# root, even when not declared as direct deps). pnpm's default strict
# isolation hides them and surfaces as cryptic
# "The required package `expo-asset` cannot be found" errors during
# `eas update` / `expo export`.
#
# `node-linker=hoisted` flattens `packages/mobile/node_modules` so
# Expo's introspection works, while the rest of the workspace
# (server / pwa / mac) keeps pnpm's stricter isolation.
node-linker=hoisted
